     <div type="poem">
   <pb facs="10"/>
   <head>In Authorem Libri.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>NVper <hi>Adamsonus</hi> vicit splendore Triones,</l>
      <l>At nunc occid<gap reason="illegible" resp="#apex" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>m spissior umbra tegit.</l>
      <l>Non tamen in caecas omnino evanuit auras,</l>
      <l>Liquerat en patrio lumina clara solo.</l>
      <l>Perthigenasque suos secus hand intermicat ille,</l>
      <l>(Accendens radio nobiliore diom)</l>
      <l>Ac Phoebe, reliquis praefulgens lu<gap reason="illegible" resp="#apex" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>ida stellis,</l>
      <l>Noctigenam pleno dum movet orbe facem.</l>
   </lg>
</div>
